text: Mighty Med is an American television series created by Jim Bernstein and Andy Schwartz. It was produced by It's a Laugh Productions for Disney XD. It stars Bradley Steven Perry, Jake Short, Paris Berelc, Devan Leos, and Augie Isaac. The series aired from October 7, 2013 to September 9, 2015.
